=== 家庭影院 ===
1983年，派拉蒙发行了《可汗怒吼》的[[VHS|VHS]]影带。同当时发行的其他影带不同，派拉蒙将《可汗怒吼》的影带定价为39.95美元，要比当时的平均价格低40多美元。这次发行被认为加剧了VHS市场的价格竞争，并推动了平价录影机的普及。<ref name="adweek-vhs">{{cite news|last=Sharkey|first=Betsy|date=1984-12-17|title=''Billion-Dollar VCR Boom Stuffs Agency Stockings''|work=Adweek|}}</ref>

2000年，派拉蒙发行了《可汗怒吼》的DVD版本，但这一版的碟片中并未包含任何特色内容。<ref>{{cite news|last=Kirkland|first=Bruce|date=2000-07-01|title=Trekking to DVD|title_zh=旅行至DVD|work={{link-en|多伦多太阳报|The Toronto Sun}}|page=36页}}</ref> 蒙塔尔万在[[加利福尼亚州|加里福尼亚州]]的[[环球城|环球城]]举行了签名售碟活动，吸引了数百名爱好者前往。<ref>{{cite  web|author=Staff|others=Stone, Sandy（照片）|date=2000-07-12|url=http://www.startrek.com/startrek/view/news/article/112011.html|title=''Dispatch: The Autograph of Khan''|work=StarTrek.com|publisher=[[维亚康姆|维亚康姆]]|accessdate=2008-10-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030815141216/http://www.startrek.com/startrek/view/news/article/112011.html|archivedate=2003-08-15}}</ref> 2002年8月，派拉蒙在众望所归下重新发行了<ref>{{cite news|last=McKay|first=John|date=2001-12-07|title=DVDs soaring in popularity|work=《[[蒙特利尔公报|蒙特利尔公报]]》|page=F4}}</ref> 由两张DVD组成的《可汗怒吼》导演版。<ref name="ign-collector">{{cite web|last=Conrad|first=Jeremy|date=2002-07-26|url=http://dvd.ign.com/articles/366/366006p1.html|title=''Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan - The Director's Edition''|title_zh=星际旅行II：可汗怒吼－导演版|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=2008-09-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080927094458/http://dvd.ign.com/articles/366/366006p1.html|archivedate=2008-09-27}}</ref>“导演版”对画面进行了数码重制，并加入了5.1[[杜比實驗室|杜比]]{{link-en|环绕声|surround sound}}声道；而第二张DVD则包括了导演评论、演员采访、[[分鏡|分镜]]画面及预告片等众多花絮内容。<ref name="ign-collector2">{{cite web|last=Conrad|first=Jeremy|date=2002-07-26|url=http://dvd.ign.com/articles/366/366006p2.html|title=''Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan - The Director's Edition (page 2)''|title_zh=星际旅行II：可汗怒吼－导演版（第2页）|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=2008-09-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090412150614/http://dvd.ign.com/articles/366/366006p2.html|archivedate=2009-04-12}}</ref> 在该版DVD发行前，重新剪辑后的电影亦先在好莱坞举行了首映。迈耶提到，他并不觉得导演剪辑版要比原来的版本好多少，但觉得重发行至少给了他一个机会，让他可以把影院版中被删掉的一些元素加回去。<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff|date=2002-08-01|url=http://www.startrek.com/startrek/view/news/article/125240.html|title=''Meyer, Montalban Unveil "Khan" Director's Cut''|work=StarTrek.com|publisher=[[维亚康姆|维亚康姆]]|accessdate=2008-10-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081014201845/http://www.startrek.com/startrek/view/news/article/125240.html|archivedate=2008-10-14}}</ref> 加长的导演剪辑版及其长达4小时的附加内容收到了不错的反响。<ref name="ign-collector2"/><ref>{{cite news|author=Staff|date=2002-05-17|title=Trek II out on DVD|work=《{{link-en|多伦多太阳报|The Toronto Sun}}》|page=86页}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Staff|date=2002-11-30|title=Essentials: Top five sci-fi films on DVD|work=《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》|page=7页}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Frank|first=Alan|date=2002-01-04|title=Alan Frank's Video View|work=《{{link-en|明星日报 (英国)|Daily Star (United Kingdom)|明星日报}}》|page=33页}}</ref>
<!-- http://www.startrek.com/startrek/view/news/article/125294.html  -->

2009年5月，隨著系列重啟新片《[[星际迷航_(电影)|星際爭霸戰]]》的上映，片商推出《可汗怒吼》院線版的[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]，與其他五部原始系列電影合體發售。<ref name="BD TC">{{cite web|author=Pascale, Anthony|date=2009-02-16|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/02/16/cbs-paramount-announce-first-star-trek-blu-ray-sets-tos-s1-all-tos-movies-coming-aprilmay/|title=TrekMovie: CBS & Paramount Announce First Star Trek Blu-ray sets – TOS S1 & All TOS movies coming April/May|publisher=TrekMovie|accessdate=2009-05-15|archive-date=2011-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111021002603/http://trekmovie.com/2009/02/16/cbs-paramount-announce-first-star-trek-blu-ray-sets-tos-s1-all-tos-movies-coming-aprilmay/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在六部原始系列電影中，只有該片以[[1080p|1080p]]高畫質重新修復。對於大規模修復的原因，導演[[尼古拉斯·迈耶|尼古拉斯·迈耶]]表示，這是因為《可汗怒吼》的[[底片#負片|負片]]「狀況相當糟糕」{{noteTag|1=原文：“[negative] was in terrible shape”．}}。<ref name="BD TC"/>此外，該藍光光碟中也包含許多全新的特別收錄，如導演迈耶和《[[星艦前傳|星艦前傳]]》製作人{{link-en|曼尼·柯多|Manny Coto}}的講評。<ref name="BD TC"/><ref name="BD DC"/>2016年6月7日，导演剪辑版的[[4K解析度|4K]]高畫質藍光光碟上市，<ref name="BD DC">{{cite web|url=http://www.startrek.com/article/khan-directors-edition-coming-to-blu-ray|title=Khan Director's Edition Coming To Blu-Ray|author=Staff|website=StarTrek.com|publisher=CBS Studios International|date=2016-04-24|accessdate=2016-04-24|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205002618/https://www.startrek.com/article/khan-directors-edition-coming-to-blu-ray|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Star-Trek-II-Directors-Blu-ray/dp/B01AI7QPM6|title=Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan Director's Cut|website=[[亞馬遜公司|Amazon.com]]|accessdate=2019-08-05|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124040056/https://www.amazon.com/Star-Trek-II-Directors-Blu-ray/dp/B01AI7QPM6|dead-url=no}}</ref>特別收錄中包含一部全新的電影製作紀錄片。<ref name="BD DC2">{{cite web|url=https://trekmovie.com/2016/06/05/twok-dc-bd-review/|title=The Wrath of Khan – Director’s Cut — Blu-ray Review|first=Matt|last=Wright|website=StarTrek.com|publisher=CBS Studios International|date=2016-06-05|accessdate=2019-08-05|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124033421/https://trekmovie.com/2016/06/05/twok-dc-bd-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

